sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Training Operator Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Controller as Training Controller<br/>Manager
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Master as Training Master Pod<br/>23456/TCP
    participant Worker as Training Worker Pods<br/>23456/TCP
    participant Storage as Object Storage S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collector

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: Training Job Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST PyTorchJob CR<br/>Auth: User Credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-kubeflow-org-v1-pytorchjob<br/>mTLS (K8s API Server)
    Webhook->>Webhook: Validate Job Spec<br/>(replicas, resources, etc)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response (OK/Reject)
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created/Rejected

    Note over Controller,Worker: Flow 2: Resource Creation
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch PyTorchJob CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: New PyTorchJob Event
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Master Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterIP Services<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup (if gang sched)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Job Status<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Kubelet,Worker: Flow 3: Training Execution
    Kubelet->>Registry: Pull Training Image<br/>HTTPS, Pull Secret
    Registry-->>Kubelet: Image Layers
    Kubelet->>Master: Start Master Pod
    Kubelet->>Worker: Start Worker Pods

    Master->>Worker: Establish Training Cluster<br/>TCP/23456, Framework-specific
    Worker->>Master: Sync Gradients<br/>TCP/23456
    Master->>Worker: Broadcast Parameters<br/>TCP/23456

    Worker->>Storage: Load Training Data<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
    Storage-->>Worker: Training Dataset
    Worker->>Storage: Save Model Checkpoints<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM

    Note over Master,Worker: Flow 4: Training Completion
    Master->>Master: Training Complete
    Worker->>Worker: Workers Complete
    Master->>Storage: Save Final Model<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Job Status<br/>Status: Succeeded

    Note over Controller,Prometheus: Flow 5: Metrics Collection
    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Operator Metrics<br/>(jobs created, succeeded, failed)

    Note over Webhook,K8sAPI: Flow 6: Certificate Rotation
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Secret<br/>training-operator-webhook-cert<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update ValidatingWebhookConfiguration<br/>caBundle field<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: Reload TLS Cert
